1. Svake nedelje imam *časove* engleskog jezika. (Every week I have *classes* of English language.)
2. Danas ću imati tri *časa* matematike. (Today I will have three *hours* of mathematics.)
3. Molim vas da me obavestite o promeni *časova*. (Please inform me about the change of *classes*.)
4. Tražim nekoga da mi drži *časove* klavira. (I am looking for someone to give me piano *lessons*.)
5. Deca su se zabavljala tokom *časa* fizičkog vaspitanja. (Children were having fun during the *physical education class*.)
6. Nisam mogao da prisustvujem *času* srpskog jezika zbog bolesti. (I couldn't attend the *Serbian language class* due to illness.)
7. Danas sam propustio *časove* zbog saobraćajne gužve. (Today I missed *classes* due to traffic jam.)
8. Da li možete da mi kažete kada su *časovi* istorije? (Can you tell me when are the *history classes*?)
9. Učenik je odlično uradio zadatak tokom *časa* matematike. (The student did an excellent job on the task during the *math class*.)
10. Nakon *časova* idem u teretanu. (After *classes* I go to the gym.)